<!-- Info Banner -->
<div class="info-banner info-banner-bg">
  <div class="info-banner-title">
    <h1>产品</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="info-container bg-white">
    <div class="content-card card-reverse">
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h4 class="text-larger text-bold">医药产品</h4>
          <p>长风药业专注于吸入制剂领域的仿制药和新药产品的开发，主要剂型包括:</p>
          <ul class="bulleted-list">
            <li><%= link_to "气雾剂", "#{dosage_forms_path}#MDI" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "鼻喷剂", "#{dosage_forms_path}#Nasal-Spray" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "雾化剂", "#{dosage_forms_path}#Nebulizer" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "干粉剂", "#{dosage_forms_path}#DPI" %></li>
          </ul>
          <p>长风研制的一些仿制药目前已在中国申报。</p>
          <p>长风的新药开发，包括新化合物研究(NCE)、新装置技术、新固定剂量复方制剂产品。</p>
<!--           <p><%= link_to "更多", new_drug_products_path, class: "btn-flat" %></p> -->
          <p><%= link_to "更多", zh_generic_drug_products_path, class: "btn-flat" %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-image-area">
        <%= image_tag "products/pharmaceutical-products", alt: "alttext", class: "card-image" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-image-area">
        <%= image_tag "products/consumer-products", alt: "alttext", class: "card-image" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h4 class="text-larger text-bold">护理产品</h4>
          <p>长风药业能为消费者提供专业、实用的呼吸系统护理产品。</p>
          <p>我们的护理品牌清氛<sup>TM</sup>系列种类齐全，能全方位满足市场的需求。</p>
          <p><%= link_to "更多", zh_consumer_products_path, class: "btn-flat" %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
